"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/w89xJ0C3rK5tO9ydo-yPG.png?height=357&width=645)\\n\\nCredix 是一个由 Solana 区块链技术提供支持的去中心化信贷市场。协议使新兴市场的贷款发起人（例如金融科技公司）能够在全球范围内获得有效的低抵押贷款，并为投资者提供固定收益投资机会。Credix 将传统金融和 DeFi 与机构所需的合规框架联系起来。\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/f-W5MPvW-RFiXIDbs93_E.png?height=197&width=697)\\n\\n## 下面讲下测试教程\\n\\n1）Phanton幻影钱包插件(直接谷歌浏览器下载安装）然后钱包里面更改测试网络\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/7Ry5aRM1TlxAMYwufLIOE.png?height=241&width=324)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/r6ZP2aOqORMTTkUC6XgJ0.png?height=471&width=333)\\n\\n2）领取[测试币](https://spl-token-faucet.com/?token-name=USDC)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/TwANMS9ZFcoi0ZbKsJ56P.png?height=585&width=634)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/UZRzKW7nta04I3VXtM5dg.png?height=541&width=528)\\n\\n3)开始正式测试，进入[测试网页](https://app.credix.finance/)，连接幻影钱包\\n\\n![页面上也可以进入刚才地址领取测试币](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/JnOKugB9VVBpHQRceTVwv.png?height=351&width=735)\\n\\n4）把USDC存入\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/MRy4KPo260idYkocArhX3.png?height=561&width=1764)\\n\\n5）借款\\n\\n左下角点击Borrow\\n\\n![点击借款（Borrow）](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/0if5uDGfqGnfJmYmnl7YR.png?height=897&width=1623)\\n\\n![输入借款USDC的数量200 利息1个点 结款周期30天，执行借款](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/i4MZ0tkgbBKomIsxeoF8B.png?height=899&width=1011)\\n\\n![](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/jRbvr2bReEhDzDX9AfbpL.png?height=827&width=1382)\\n\\n6）还款\\n\\n![执行还款操作 USDC手续费数量2 进行支付](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/IURVpeG4eggMyhw_2QdIx.png?height=759&width=1236)\\n\\n![借款200，还款成功 完成借贷的USDC数量100](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/6gL3dXWKPDIcnRf_ypRZY.png?height=813&width=1273)\\n\\n以上就是Credix测试网交互教程。\\n\\n想了就更多欢迎加入追风社区交流： \\n TG：<https://t.me/CryptoDigger88> \\n 币用：<https://0.plus/CryptoDigger88> \\n Dis： <https://discord.gg/djHttK592U> \\n Twitter：[@ZF_lab](https://twitter.com/ZF_lab)\",\"timestamp\":1641215966,\"title\":\"Credix测试教程\"},\"digest\":\"zEapDAb3-WpPLTkj7IcoWfJRccMg9nAcgs2A8WQ3wyk\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x232F9B36Fb579a71034dc21A467c921eec01FAA9\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"q3G1pFxUQxAjc7n1BpuOdIyi5OPkngh__hNUPF4bwNk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xg2td5GN7KgLaTDM9H9sPU6iTzvVoBzNzfOzdVPgJRo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"Wh1mQ_K1o-w5gaKni2neSLkD0GVHDWqqYM8H89M-7FSu8oNsQaUEW2KFQizHeUmE_dlU4UII4Qg_ezvHoNT0OQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xbe0b8139cc8d6535086008b730f3472efdf604fcbd3cf21b05b4391f266dcc214b40849e4e0d31c7c312ab5838857f5039bbc41adbe198262e44df581a0a2d6b1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"q3G1pFxUQxAjc7n1BpuOdIyi5OPkngh__hNUPF4bwNk\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"xg2td5GN7KgLaTDM9H9sPU6iTzvVoBzNzfOzdVPgJRo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"zEapDAb3-WpPLTkj7IcoWfJRccMg9nAcgs2A8WQ3wyk\"}"